cdata.name: UnitaryStatus Dollar
cdata.desc: USDe is another scrypt crypto currency - branding itself as an anti establishmentarian - anti Fed - and pro liberty in the American sense. The coin has two block reward reductions when 1/3 of supply has been mined. Total supply is 1.6bn. The coin is scrypt (anti asic mining) with single block difficulty retargetting using the kimoto gravity well. Inital block reward is set at 4000.
